ZH: 我们每年都会捐款给慈善机构。
EN: We donate to charity organizations every year.

ZH: 她捐款给了地震灾区。
EN: She donated to the earthquake-stricken area.

ZH: 请考虑捐款支持这个项目。
EN: Please consider making a donation to support this project.

ZH: 他一直在募集捐款帮助癌症患者。
EN: He has been raising donations to help cancer patients.

ZH: 很多人都愿意捐款救助有需要的人。
EN: Many people are willing to donate to help those in need.

ZH: 这笔捐款将用于帮助改善当地教育条件。
EN: This donation will be used to help improve local education conditions.

ZH: 她的慷慨捐款帮助了很多无家可归的人。
EN: Her generous donation has helped many homeless people.

ZH: 每一笔捐款都能帮助改善社会。
EN: Every donation can help improve society.

ZH: 请大家共同捐款帮助灾区。
EN: Please everyone donate together to help the disaster area.

ZH: 我们将发起募款活动，希望获得更多捐款。
EN: We will launch a fundraising campaign in hopes of receiving more donations.

ZH: 感谢您的善举和慷慨捐款。
EN: Thank you for your kindness and generous donation.

ZH: 这次捐款是我们社区的共同努力。
EN: This donation is a collective effort from our community.

