ZH: 这位慈善家每年捐款给数十家慈善机构。
EN: This philanthropist donates to dozens of charity organizations every year.

ZH: 感谢您对我们项目的慷慨捐款。
EN: Thank you for your generous donation to our project.

ZH: 请向受困者伸出援手，捐款帮助他们重新站起来。
EN: Please reach out to the distressed and donate to help them stand up again.

ZH: 祖父辛苦工作一生，留下了一大笔捐款给慈善事业。
